    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3><a href="https://twitter.com/baldwindavid">David Baldwin</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/ar3_me">Andrew L Robinson III</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/mileszs">Miles Sterrett</a> - Unconventional Rails Objects</h3>

<p>We discuss some of the objects written into Rails applications we work with that are not common in Rails. We talk a bit about our thoughts on them, and lead a discussion for the whole group.</p>

<p><a href="http://podcast.404dev.com/episodes/088_Unconventional_Rails_Objects.mp3">Audio</a> (1h : 37m)</p>

<p>Links to other stuff discussed and post-discussion from the mailing list:</p>

<ul>
